        Ic-BL) core-collapse SNe. We use photometric and spectroscopic
        data for 67 core-collapse SNe from the literature, and for each
        generate a time-series spectral template. The techniques used to
        build the templates are fully data driven with no assumption of
        any parametric form or model for the light curves. The template-
        building code is open source, and can be applied to any
